><blockquote>搭單認真問 100日abs有冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中六基本上冇返過學<br />\nabs 1xx<br />\n入到大學，jupas個個self introduction冇做到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以問下巴打幾多分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483a5679f393ada2a061a44968e50f5af64fdfb6","tid":26291,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:10:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f99e4380ee17fdbcef52c2b8b94bde96b106491","tid":26291,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單認真問 100日abs有冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中六基本上冇返過學<br />\nabs 1xx<br />\n入到大學，jupas個個self introduction冇做到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自學成才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學校點睇？<br />\n利申個個月真病睇醫生計埋十幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nband 3 尾學校<br />\n返學好撚嘈，呀sir冇心教<br />\n係屋企一日溫4-5個鐘書<br />\n儲到一堆問題就返學問呀sir<br />\n<br />\n唔返學太多比學校勸我退學，<br />\n點知最尾我係成間學校5個入到大學之一（其餘4個係外校repeat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實banding無乜問題<br />\n通常老師加同學先會搞到唔想返學<br />\n仆街同學當睇唔到<br />\n班老屎忽成日踩尻學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係姑婆黨陰陰濕濕咁<br />\n仲有堆教畜用成績標籤學生<br />\n差嗰堆=廢柴垃圾<br />\n甚至話你樣有問題腦有問題所以讀書唔掂<br />\n望住隔離學校band3但係日日開心過都幾羨慕<br />\n自由不在話下 老師無咁大架子又肯陪學生玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我嗰間似監倉多啲<br />\n就算band3都好 有心讀去到邊都一樣<br />\n就算band1一樣有人DSE拎5分6分好多仆街好黑暗<br />\n利申 所謂band1女校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學校分banding根本on9 <br />\n利申2 留過級之後讀書讀到寸返當年叫我退選修科個廢中"},{"pid":"94be35a76c15cc356b3bba02d1baf29454936617","tid":26291,"uid":42795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"我記過小過添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾DSE 4+2 34咪又入到HKU<br />\n一句到尾:成績至上"},{"pid":"3b4a31adb1391f4ddaeb959f4e3c194e0f2e28ec","tid":26291,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"我中六有小過 我報eapp 照upload左有小過嘅成績表 一樣都收左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}